{"tid":1581413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夾硬忘記一個人真係好攰","createTime":"2019-09-19T14:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T01:43:51.000Z","uid":85934,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"841c21df7474ee63ae927ca69d1bb0408a78c1ba","tid":1581413,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:19:10.000Z","msg":"大家可能都鍾意大家，但係因為好多原因，我做錯過，佢亦錯過，或者大家都唔想再受傷而唔敢再行前一步，最後大家回歸陌路人，互不認識，我亦因為咁而離開咗一個同佢一齊嘅地方，重新過生活。<br />\n<br />\n雖然好似每日都好正常，但其實我發夢仲會見到佢，都仲會諗起佢，而家我因為咁而有情緒病。唉。一直好想搵佢，但係之前試過都唔成功，我都冇勇氣再搵佢，好似自己唔掂就唔好再害人。<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦，好攰"},{"pid":"7f315a6ac44f1d2c29891b3efc005467848509a2","tid":1581413,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c40dbeed33d2962d0907075325fde7791975305","tid":1581413,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=e983ac5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=dc57e13a\" target=\